<template>
  <v-card class="d-inline-block mx-auto">
    <v-container>
      <v-row justify="space-between">
        <v-col
          cols="auto"
          class="text-center pl-0"
        >

          <v-row
            class="flex-column ma-0 fill-height"
            justify="center"
          >
            <v-col class="px-0">
                <v-text-field label="Name" v-model="name"></v-text-field>
            </v-col>

            <v-col class="px-0">
              <v-text-field label="Tel" v-model="tel"></v-text-field>
            </v-col>

            <v-col class="px-0">
              <v-text-field label="Address" v-model="address"></v-text-field>
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>

      <v-card-actions class="align-end">
            <v-spacer/>
            <v-btn color="primary">생성</v-btn>
            <v-btn class="btn deleteBtn" color="error">취소</v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-container>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import { mapActions, mapState } from 'vuex'
export default {
  data () {
    return {
      no: 0,
      name: '',
      tel: '',
      address: ''
    }
  },

  computed: {
    ...mapState({
      contact: (state) => state.contacts.contact
    })
  },
  methods: {
    ...mapActions(['getContact'])
  },
  created () {
    this.getContact(this.$route.params.no)
    console.log(this.contact)
    this.no = this.contact.no
    this.name = this.contact.name
    this.tel = this.contact.tel
    this.address = this.contact.address
  },
  beforeCreate () {

  }
}
</script>
